claim.claim-text:
A polymeric fastener (10; 90), comprising:
a body (12) adapted to receive a tool induced rotational torque;
a flange (16) integrally connected to the body (12);
a wave-shaped washer (20; 92) integrally connected to the flange (16), the wave-shaped washer (20; 92) having multiple valleys (22) interposed between multiple oppositely directed peaks (24); and
multiple frangible connectors (26) integrally connecting the flange (16) to the wave-shaped washer (20; 92), each frangible connector (26) integrally connected at a first end (25) to the flange (16), and integrally connected at an opposite connecting tip (33) to an individual one of the peaks (24).
